   AGGREGATE LIABILITY SHALL NOT EXCEED FEES PAID BY CUSTOMER FOR THE
   LICENSE KEY GIVING RISE TO THE CLAIM.

8. COMPLIANCE & AUDIT
   Upon thirty (30) days’ written notice, Cybersage may audit Customer’s
   deployment to verify compliance. Customer shall cooperate and, if an
   audit reveals non‑compliance, promptly pay additional fees plus
   reasonable audit costs.

9. EXPORT CONTROL
   Customer shall not export or re‑export the Software except in
   compliance with U.S. export control laws and regulations and those of
